                            <p className="text-[rgb(229,231,235)] text-[18px] leading-[28px] absolute left-[0px] top-[31px] box-border m-0 w-[854.359375px] h-[77px] overflow-hidden text-clip">
                              A few years ago, the "YouTube automation" dream meant endless tabs, expensive editors, rejected freelancers, stock-site rabbit holes, and missed upload days. Channels died not because ideas were bad, but because consistency is a monster when you're doing everything manually.
                            </p>
